Class Series

java.lang.Object

      com.google.gwt.visualization.client.visualizations.corechart.Series

public class Series
extends com.google.gwt.core.client.JavaScriptObject

Series specifications for Chart Options. The ComboChart is the primary user of series. Color-related draw options accept either the name of the color as a string, or the detailed color specification.

See Also:
Combo Configuration Options Reference
